    "nom_orig": "Maya",
    "texte_orig": "Wow![SP]Looks[SP]like[SP]the[SP]party's[SP]in[SP]full[SP]swing.\nThis[SP]seems[SP]pretty[SP]upscale[SP]for[SP]a[SP]high[SP]school\nfestival.",
